s such, provides an important avenue for monitoring and development of vaccines against major bat-borne viruses both in the reservoir and spillover hosts. Additionally, it will provide a foundation to understand the role of adaptive immunity in bat antiviral responses.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Wynne, James W.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Woon, Amanda P.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Dudek, Nadine L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Croft, Nathan P.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ng, Justin H. J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Baker, Michelle L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Wang, Lin-Fa", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Purcell, Anthony W.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/fbbc7615976884dc5440db36946d4647", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/3731b90237aa939c2802dce0bd2dd2f0fad90d6a737ef1d0ebe9418da685747f", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/7YX2MQKN", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/7YX2MQKN", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/81eea6c28e4dbcca044aa322d627547b!/b118695-121156", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "11", "pages": "4468-4476", "title": "The Journal of Immunology", "volume": "19